<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 14:07:55 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>维基百科编辑总结：以色列正在加沙实施种族灭绝</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/english-wikipedia-editors-concluded-israel-is-committing-genocide-in-gaza/00000191-321a-d4dc-a397-bf1e3fba0000</link><description>自从世界上最受欢迎的在线网站的编辑上个月投票决定将维基百科条目重命名为“加沙种族灭绝”并删除了之前的“指控”一词以来，该条目每天都有数以万计的浏览量</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 13:43:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/english-wikipedia-editors-concluded-israel-is-committing-genocide-in-gaza/00000191-321a-d4dc-a397-bf1e3fba0000</guid></item><item><title>选择辛瓦尔作为政治领袖巩固了战争而非外交作为哈马斯命运的关键</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/choosing-sinwar-as-political-chief-cements-war-not-diplomacy-as-key-to-hamas-fate/00000191-319c-dc5a-adf5-33be8fef0000</link><description>辛瓦尔被任命为哈马斯政治局局长应被视为一种意向宣言：哈马斯明白，加沙实地发生的事情比外交更能决定战争的结果，因此将权力移交给了当地政府。地面指挥部</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 12:14:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/choosing-sinwar-as-political-chief-cements-war-not-diplomacy-as-key-to-hamas-fate/00000191-319c-dc5a-adf5-33be8fef0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列撤销八名挪威外交官在巴勒斯坦权力机构的地位，作为承认巴勒斯坦的惩罚</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/israel-revokes-eight-norwegian-diplomats-status-as-punishment-for-recognizing-palestine/00000191-317f-d4dc-a397-bd7f882d0000</link><description>以色列外交部宣布撤销八名挪威外交官的外交身份，这将有效阻止挪威在以色列和约旦河西岸的活动；挪威：“这是一种极端行为”</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 11:38:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/israel-revokes-eight-norwegian-diplomats-status-as-punishment-for-recognizing-palestine/00000191-317f-d4dc-a397-bd7f882d0000</guid></item><item><title>血液、柴油和发电机：以色列的医疗系统如何为与真主党的战争做准备</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/blood-and-generators-how-israels-healthcare-system-is-preparing-for-war-with-hezbollah/00000191-3123-d1b4-a399-7da714850000</link><description>“我们现在不储存的东西在与真主党的战争期间不会存在”：以色列各地的医院正在通过储存医疗和手术用品、数千单位的血液以及柴油和汽油来为战争做准备</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 10:56:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/blood-and-generators-how-israels-healthcare-system-is-preparing-for-war-with-hezbollah/00000191-3123-d1b4-a399-7da714850000</guid></item><item><title>以色列做出具有里程碑意义的决定，授予乌干达犹太人公民身份</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/israel-grants-citizenship-to-ugandan-jew-in-landmark-decision/00000191-2dd1-d1b4-a399-7df7ac820000</link><description>七年四次皈依：乌干达阿巴尤达亚社区的成员约瑟夫·基比塔（Yosef Kibita）进行了一场漫长的法律斗争，以获得作为犹太人移民的资格</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 10:47:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/israel-grants-citizenship-to-ugandan-jew-in-landmark-decision/00000191-2dd1-d1b4-a399-7df7ac820000</guid></item><item><title>高级官员表示，以色列警方不会调查极右翼暴徒袭击以色列国防军基地的事件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/police-arent-investigating-storming-of-idf-bases-by-far-right-mobs-senior-officer-says/00000191-3153-d4e2-a9dd-b37f214f0000</link><description>极右翼示威者闯入斯德泰曼和拜特利德的以色列军事基地，那里关押着涉嫌虐待巴勒斯坦被拘留者的以色列国防军士兵，一周半后，没有人受到讯问或逮捕——尽管冲突被媒体捕捉到。视频</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 10:22:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/police-arent-investigating-storming-of-idf-bases-by-far-right-mobs-senior-officer-says/00000191-3153-d4e2-a9dd-b37f214f0000</guid></item><item><title>“我和你一起去”：本格维尔的警察局长在泄露的录音中宣誓效忠极右翼部长</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/im-with-you-ben-gvir-police-chief-pick-vows-allegiance-to-minister-in-leaked-recording/00000191-30d6-d386-adff-7dde8bf50000</link><description>在《国土报》获得的录音中，伊塔马尔·本·格维尔挑选的警察局长表示，尽管遭到以色列警方和内塔尼亚胡办公室的正式反对，他仍将支持拆除德鲁兹人的房屋</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 09:32:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/im-with-you-ben-gvir-police-chief-pick-vows-allegiance-to-minister-in-leaked-recording/00000191-30d6-d386-adff-7dde8bf50000</guid></item><item><title>美国希望阻止伊朗对以色列的重大袭击，而真主党仍然是未知因素</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/fearing-catastrophic-war-biden-warns-iran-against-attack-pushes-pm-to-make-deal/00000191-2de7-da6f-af99-2de71f1d0000</link><description>美国和以色列官员相信，真主党对杀害一名高级官员的报复将集中在军事地点，但他们不能肯定地说，真主党会多么谨慎地避免伤害平民</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 03:00:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/fearing-catastrophic-war-biden-warns-iran-against-attack-pushes-pm-to-make-deal/00000191-2de7-da6f-af99-2de71f1d0000</guid></item><item><title>现在发号施令，辛瓦尔的接管不会改变以色列与哈马斯协议的条款</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/sinwars-promotion-likely-wont-change-in-hamas-stance-in-hostage-talks-with-israel/00000191-2e07-d1b4-a399-7ea78a9c0000</link><description>辛瓦尔作为哈马斯政治局局长的新角色，负责监督军事和政治部门，这并没有改变以色列与哈马斯协议的动态，目前正在等待内塔尼亚胡的回应。他的任命是为了确保哈马斯的政治和财政未来，这可能比军事挑战更重要</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 03:00:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/sinwars-promotion-likely-wont-change-in-hamas-stance-in-hostage-talks-with-israel/00000191-2e07-d1b4-a399-7ea78a9c0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡很想解雇他的国防部长，但不相信其他选择</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-would-love-to-boot-his-defense-minister-but-doesnt-trust-the-alternative/00000191-2e3c-da6f-af99-2e7e6c7d0000</link><description>由于大多数联盟认为全面的地区战争是一个有价值的目标，总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡似乎将坚持国防部长约阿夫·加兰特 — — 至少目前如此</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 03:00:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-would-love-to-boot-his-defense-minister-but-doesnt-trust-the-alternative/00000191-2e3c-da6f-af99-2e7e6c7d0000</guid></item><item><title>在《时代》杂志采访中，内塔尼亚胡否认了 10 月 7 日问责制问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article-live/u-s-says-cease-fire-deal-closer-than-ever-cnn-hezbollah-could-attack-israel-without-iran/00000191-2fb9-d759-a795-bfff7dd90000</link><description>以色列撤销挪威驻巴勒斯坦权力机构特使的外交地位，作为对巴勒斯坦承认的惩罚 ■ 报告：真主党可能会先于伊朗攻击以色列；德黑兰“重新考虑”报复范围 ■ 伊朗外长表示，将在“适当的时间以适当的方式”作出回应 ■ 加拿大批准将外交官的子女和监护人临时迁出以色列 ■ 策划约旦河西岸恐怖袭击的哈马斯高级成员以色列国防军称在加沙被杀</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 02:13:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article-live/u-s-says-cease-fire-deal-closer-than-ever-cnn-hezbollah-could-attack-israel-without-iran/00000191-2fb9-d759-a795-bfff7dd90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列右翼声称受到迫害。这是无耻的谎言</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-right-wing-claims-to-be-persecuted-its-a-shameless-lie/00000191-2d8c-d200-a9f9-adcd6e7a0000</link><description>对某些人不平等地运用法律，同时又不让其他人承担责任的做法可以追溯到以色列，但不是针对右翼</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 20:18:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-right-wing-claims-to-be-persecuted-its-a-shameless-lie/00000191-2d8c-d200-a9f9-adcd6e7a0000</guid></item><item><title>美国：“比以往任何时候都更接近”加沙停火；西方外交官称谈判仍陷入僵局</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/u-s-closer-than-ever-to-cease-fire-in-gaza-western-diplomats-say-talks-still-stuck/00000191-2e0e-d4e9-a7b7-2fce7d1c0000</link><description>国家安全委员会发言人约翰·柯比声称协议已经摆在桌面上，但参与以色列与哈马斯谈判的西方外交官否认了解谈判取得突破</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 19:45:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/u-s-closer-than-ever-to-cease-fire-in-gaza-western-diplomats-say-talks-still-stuck/00000191-2e0e-d4e9-a7b7-2fce7d1c0000</guid></item><item><title>在以色列最后的常态堡垒中，紧张地等待伊朗的报复</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-07/ty-article/.highlight/in-israels-last-bastions-of-normalcy-waiting-nervously-for-irans-revenge/00000191-2d53-d1b4-a399-7df7cc470000</link><description>这种等待的游戏是攻击的一部分——哈桑·纳斯鲁拉甚至说过同样的话——也许伊朗和真主党希望悬念确实会杀死我们</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 18:48:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-07/ty-article/.highlight/in-israels-last-bastions-of-normalcy-waiting-nervously-for-irans-revenge/00000191-2d53-d1b4-a399-7df7cc470000</guid></item><item><title>美国犹太人在观看以色列的犹太至上主义暴徒时并没有感到更安全</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-08-07/ty-article-opinion/.premium/u-s-jews-dont-feel-safer-when-they-watch-israels-jewish-supremacist-mobs/00000191-2806-dbbc-ab95-3957c76c0000</link><description>如果以色列想继续成为所有犹太人的家园，就不能放松对保护所有人的民主自由价值观的警惕</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 17:33:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-08-07/ty-article-opinion/.premium/u-s-jews-dont-feel-safer-when-they-watch-israels-jewish-supremacist-mobs/00000191-2806-dbbc-ab95-3957c76c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 306 天：世卫组织将向加沙运送超过 100 万支脊髓灰质炎疫苗</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-306-who-to-send-gaza-over-one-million-polio-vaccines/00000191-2dbe-da6f-af99-2dfe6cee0001</link><description>白宫表示，“我们距离达成我们所认为的最接近”的人质释放/停火协议 ■ 据报道，联黎部队官员的家属已从黎巴嫩撤离 ■ 土耳其正式要求加入南非对国际法院的诉讼，指控以色列在叙利亚实施种族灭绝加沙 ■ 德国和法国拒绝接受以色列财政部长的言论，即让 200 万加沙人挨饿是“正确且道德的” ■ 战争已过去 306 天，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 17:00:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-306-who-to-send-gaza-over-one-million-polio-vaccines/00000191-2dbe-da6f-af99-2dfe6cee0001</guid></item><item><title>以色列新闻频道忠实内塔尼亚胡首席执行官因记者强烈反对而被撤换</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/newly-appointed-ceo-of-israeli-new-channel-to-be-replaced-after-journalists-backlash/00000191-2d8e-d1b4-a399-7dae6d8f0000</link><description>尤利娅·沙马洛夫-贝尔科维奇被任命为以色列第 13 频道的负责人是有争议的，因为她公开支持内塔尼亚胡的立场，但在她被记录说“电视台里有很多坏记者”后，员工的反抗导致该频道宣布她将被任命为以色列第 13 频道的负责人。被取代</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 16:47:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/newly-appointed-ceo-of-israeli-new-channel-to-be-replaced-after-journalists-backlash/00000191-2d8e-d1b4-a399-7dae6d8f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列部长与 Black Cube 就监视亲巴勒斯坦的美国学生团体举行会谈</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-minister-held-talks-with-black-cube-about-spying-on-pro-palestinian-u-s-students/00000191-2d2b-d927-a5b5-ff7f03690000</link><description>侨民事务部长 Amichai Chikli 于 6 月会见 Black Cube，讨论可能对巴勒斯坦学生正义组织执行间谍任务，该组织在美国校园领导反以色列抗议活动。该部称 Black Cube 向其提出了这个想法，但消息人士称事实恰恰相反</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 15:19:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-minister-held-talks-with-black-cube-about-spying-on-pro-palestinian-u-s-students/00000191-2d2b-d927-a5b5-ff7f03690000</guid></item><item><title>法国和德国猛烈抨击以色列斯莫特里奇关于饿死加沙人的言论</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/france-germany-slam-israels-smotrich-for-comments-on-starving-gazans-to-death/00000191-2d2f-d4ad-a7ff-fd3fc82b0000</link><description>法国和德国外交部谴责这位右翼部长，几天前他暗示国际压力是以色列不让加沙人饿死的唯一原因</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 15:15:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/france-germany-slam-israels-smotrich-for-comments-on-starving-gazans-to-death/00000191-2d2f-d4ad-a7ff-fd3fc82b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列周围的火圈：伊朗、真主党和胡塞武装的军火库</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/the-ring-of-fire-around-israel-a-look-at-the-arsenals-of-iran-hezbollah-and-the-houthis/00000191-2ce3-d927-a5b5-ffff7b5c0000</link><description>从远程巡航导弹到携带炸弹的无人机，以色列的敌人可能会对其防空系统进行前所未有的考验</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 14:29:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/the-ring-of-fire-around-israel-a-look-at-the-arsenals-of-iran-hezbollah-and-the-houthis/00000191-2ce3-d927-a5b5-ffff7b5c0000</guid></item></channel></rss>